            <lg xml:id="TK1176">
<l>ōo viṉitē yemakkinnōy ceytakaṇ </l>
<l> ṭāa mitaṟpaṭ ṭatu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The eyes that have given me this disease have themselves been seized with this (suffering). Oh! I am much delighted.</l>
